llama3.1.reason: Despite being a costly undertaking for the Allies, two of the six merchant ships from Operation Harpoon actually completed their journey to Malta, delivering much-needed supplies, while also sinking several Axis aircraft and warships, indicating that the operation was not an Italian naval victory.
